Color Menu
Choose from 15 standard colors. 17 Basic colors, or 140+ Extended colors. Get the hex code, RGB code, or a color square on the clipboard.
Open this menu with an input of “#” or “rgb” and the menu will return the users chosen color in hex or RGB, or default is a 16 x 16 pixel color png
